      "html": "<p>也可写作 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">eastwards</i>，古英语写作 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">eastwearde</i>； 参见 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of east \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/east\">east</a> 和 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of -ward \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/-ward\">-ward</a>。作为形容词于15世纪中期出现，源自副词。</p>"
